<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 36.1 (October 7, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Bombshell (Q)</b></li><ul><li> The power ratio of the primary hit portion of this ability has been increased to 0.8, up from 0.5.</li><li> The power ratio of the splash damage portion of this ability has been increased to 0.4, up from 0.3.</li><li> The total damage of the empowered version of this ability has been reduced to 175% of a single use of this ability, down from 200%.</li></ul></ul>